8 || [[Chalay Thay Saath]] || Galaxy Lollywood Awards || Best Actor in a Leading Role Female || {{nom}} <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://galaxylollywood.com/2018/03/05/galaxylollywoodawards2018/|title=Luxus Grand 4th Galaxy Lollywood Awards 2018 (Nominations)|last=Lollywood|first=Galaxy|date=2018-03-05|website=Galaxy Lollywood|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Personal life==\nOn 21 October 2012, she married [[Shehroz Sabzwari]], son of actor [[Behroze Sabzwari]] in an [[Nikah|Islamic wedding ceremony]] in [[Karachi]].<ref>{{cite web | url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/461091/young-lovers-saira-and-shahroz-tie-the-knot/ | title=Young lovers Saira Yousuf, Shehroz Sabzwari tie the knot! | date=November 5, 2012 | accessdate=March 18, 2013}}</ref> Their daughter, Nooreh, was born in 2014.\n\nIn December 2019, the couple announced their separation and got divorced in February 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dnd.com.pk/syra-shehroz-and-shehroz-sabzwari-divorced-after-7-years-of-marriage/178687|title=Syra Shehroz and Shehroz Sabzwari Separated after 7 years of marriage|last=Mati|date=2019-12-29|website=Dispatch News Desk|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|colwidth=30em}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Shehroz, Syra}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Pakistani female models]]\n[[Category:Pakistani television actresses]]\n[[Category:Actresses from Karachi]]\n[[Category:21st-century Pakistani actresses]]\n[[Category:1988 births]]\n", "name_user": "119.152.133.60", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200ePersonal life)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syra_Yousuf"}
